  "detailed_description": "XP Soccer is a love letter to the classic soccer games from the NES era!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/723ce22934682dccc683b608a2a02321.poster.avif?t=1700483579\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/723ce22934682dccc683b608a2a02321.webm?t=1700483579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/723ce22934682dccc683b608a2a02321.mp4?t=1700483579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>We wanted to use pixel-art in a way that is faithful to the 90's console limitations, only breaking those rules sparsely to enhance the player's experience and customization.<br><br>Simple and tight controls will give you a variety of moves with a combination of the classic A and B buttons!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >56 National Teams:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/9a2fe5daa02195993ed2506f94699585.avif?t=1700483579\" width=604 height=118 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Modes:</h2>■  Exhibition Match (Single Player, Local VS and Local Co-Op)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/629b7a669f9707b94131def67f79753d.poster.avif?t=1700483579\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/629b7a669f9707b94131def67f79753d.webm?t=1700483579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/629b7a669f9707b94131def67f79753d.mp4?t=1700483579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>■  8 Tournaments (Single Player and Local Co-Op)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/885e673a45a142df4af30c09777ba165.webp?t=1700483579\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/885e673a45a142df4af30c09777ba165.poster.avif?t=1700483579\" class=\"bb_img\" width=604 height=340 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>■     56 National Teams<br>■     4 Grass Stadiums<br>■     4 Alternative Stadiums<br>■     40 Achievements<br>■     Formations and Substitutions<br>■     Curve Shots<br>■     Fouls, Free Kicks and Penalties<br>■     Simple controls<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/373b6e9e9b063c25fc85acf193a967bb.poster.avif?t=1700483579\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/373b6e9e9b063c25fc85acf193a967bb.webm?t=1700483579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/373b6e9e9b063c25fc85acf193a967bb.mp4?t=1700483579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "XP Soccer is a love letter to the classic soccer games from the NES era!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/723ce22934682dccc683b608a2a02321.poster.avif?t=1700483579\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/723ce22934682dccc683b608a2a02321.webm?t=1700483579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/723ce22934682dccc683b608a2a02321.mp4?t=1700483579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>We wanted to use pixel-art in a way that is faithful to the 90's console limitations, only breaking those rules sparsely to enhance the player's experience and customization.<br><br>Simple and tight controls will give you a variety of moves with a combination of the classic A and B buttons!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >56 National Teams:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/9a2fe5daa02195993ed2506f94699585.avif?t=1700483579\" width=604 height=118 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Modes:</h2>■  Exhibition Match (Single Player, Local VS and Local Co-Op)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/629b7a669f9707b94131def67f79753d.poster.avif?t=1700483579\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/629b7a669f9707b94131def67f79753d.webm?t=1700483579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013580/extras/629b7a669f9707b94131def67f79753d.mp4?t=1700483579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></vid